| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5946 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 50d2596f-3cab-51ea-9e0a-29af8f21e18e"
